title: bob hund - Ingenting
description:
Here it is again. It was removed during the time Pirate Bay was down.

I&#039;m too lazy to write a description again. Just fucking google it, alright? :P Or check here: www.bobhund.com

Basicly it&#039;s an album released freely on bob hund&#039;s official website (because there are so few real copies anyway). I downloaded the WAV version and compressed it to flac (a free lossless audio codec which doesn&#039;t remove audio during compression, compared to e.g. OGG and MP3). I share it here to make downloading faster for everyone (and now bobhund.com doesn&#039;t need to pay as much for their bandwidth anymore ;D ).

Information on how to decompress flac is here: flac.sourceforge.net
